WEBVTT

00:00:28.538 --> 00:00:32.482
that Steve Pinker is one of the world's
most influential minds.

00:00:32.506 --> 00:00:36.048
He's a cognitive scientist,
a psychologist, a linguist,

00:00:36.072 --> 00:00:39.706
and in recent years, has become
something of a historian

00:00:39.730 --> 00:00:41.197
and statistician also.

00:00:41.794 --> 00:00:44.633
His two most recent blockbuster books

00:00:44.657 --> 00:00:48.339
try to answer an incredibly
important question:

00:00:48.363 --> 00:00:51.483
Is the world getting better or worse?

00:00:51.863 --> 00:00:55.117
Steven Pinker (From TED 2018):
Many people face the news each morning

00:00:55.141 --> 00:00:56.926
with trepidation and dread.

00:00:56.950 --> 00:01:01.345
2016 was called the "worst year ever" --